#Plugin for confluence
<p>This plugin allows to add Macro, which give opportunity to personalize page background</p>

##How to use
###If you want add macro to own page  
1. Create new page
2. Add "ColorPick" macro on it
3. Publish page
<p>After that each user can set page background on own taste</p>

###If you want to set background
1. Choose page
2. Click Upload File button
3. Pick image
4. Enjoy:)

<p>This is alpha version of plugin and there are some fixes in near future.</p>
<p>Thanks for understanding</p>  
